title.en: First members of  Merched y Wawr Garreg Wen Branch
title.cy: Aelodau Cyntaf Merched y Wawr Y Garreg Wen

description.en:
Llun o aelodau cyntaf Merched y Wawr Cangen Y Garreg Wen ym 1974 yn Neuadd Bentref Ffostrasol.  
Rhes Gefn – Menna Davies, May Jones, Dianne Evans, Annie Jones, Etta James, Mrs Jones y Siop, Maureen Evans, Mrs Elias, Sarah Ann Davies, Sallie Williams, Morfudd Evans, Maud Evans
Rhes flaen – Lil Thomas, Morwen Evans. Elean?  Colbourne, Ray Tobias, Dilys Richards, Marlene Evans, Annie Elias, Annie Williams
